messages.message:
For the large files, added a test script that I got working at
https://github.com/instabase/benchmarks/blob/24f91dd1b60ec1203202bd83aea94e7e1bf2b0eb/scripts/large_file_test.py
The script chunks a large PDF into smaller ones. Depending on vertex-ai true or false, uploads to GCS or to gemini files. Passes all the chunks to the model and a META_JSON that contains metadata indicating which chunk is which page range. Extracts data just like today.
Large files are at https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1ET0uC4oUxHaNT6kp4wpffLCvb1mxJGOl.
There are 9 individual annual reports. Combined<n>.pdf combines n annual report. It works till combined6.pdf I think.
